layoutPrompt = "Given the text of the Arxiv paper you now have the context of, please generate a proposed structure for a Jupyter notebook that would summarize the paper's key contributions and findings. The Jupyter notebook should be structured in a logical and coherent way, with sections and sub-sections that reflect the paper's organization. Please assume that the Jupyter notebook will be used by someone who is familiar with the general field of AI, but may not be familiar with the specific topic of the paper. The output should be in a format that can be easily imported into a Jupyter notebook and customized by the user."